      dct:created "2026-06-10"^^xsd:date ;
      skos:note "Part 3 of the consulting-engagement session record (June 10-12, 2026). Scarlet Dame working session with Claude. Covers the three-phase engagement arc, ingestion mechanism redesign, cadence/calibration reframe, pricing principle, deliverables, and capacity reality." ;
